   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Your subordinate Petros allows himself the freedom to write to his master P...s. First of all, I greet my lord with devotion. I ask of you to talk to .......kores, so that he will hand out to us his men, because you are aware that he will yet again make100 dike lengths for which we are responsible.You know all the other losses that we have suffered (because of that?). The trimesion for clay: they have made bricks out of them (?), as you wished . . . "</ab>
         </div>
